description:
Electronics For You - December 2013
 English | 150 Pages | True PDF | 55MB

Electronics For You, also known as EFY or E4U, is an Indian technology-oriented magazine owned by EFY Enterprises. It has been in publication since 1969.[2] The company is head quartered in New Delhi, and has offices in Bangalore, Chennai, Kolkata and Mumbai.

The magazine is popular among many electronics engineering students in India and some of its readers have since gone ahead to make significant advances in this field. The Magazine is considered to be the Number One Electronics Magazine in South-East Asia.
